# Templates & Frontend

## Template Inheritance

All pages extend `base.html`:

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}
{% block title %}Page Title{% endblock %}
{% block head_extra %}<!-- page CSS -->{% endblock %}
{% block content %}<!-- page body -->{% endblock %}
```

## Styling

- **No CSS framework** — custom CSS with CSS variables for theming
- Theme toggle: `localStorage['chili-theme']`, `data-theme` attribute on `<html>`
- Colors via CSS variables: `--bg`, `--fg`, `--accent`, `--border`, `--card-bg`
- Dark mode: `[data-theme="dark"]` selector overrides
- Layout: flexbox and CSS grid, `max-width` containers

## JavaScript

- **Vanilla JS only** — no React, Vue, or build tools
- `fetch()` for API calls with `credentials: 'same-origin'`
- CDN libraries: `marked.js` (markdown), `highlight.js` (code), `DOMPurify` (sanitization)
- All JS is inline in template `<script>` blocks
- LightweightCharts v4 for trading charts with indicator sub-panes
- HTML5 Drag and Drop for reorderable UI elements (chart panels, etc.)

### API Call Pattern

```javascript
fetch('/api/endpoint', { method: 'POST', headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, body: JSON.stringify(data) })
  .then(r => r.json())
  .then(d => { if (!d.ok) { alert(d.error); return; } /* handle d */ })
  .catch(() => alert('Network error'));
```

### State Management

Frontend state uses module-level variables with `_` prefix:

```javascript
var _activeTab = 'overview';
var _paneSlots = ['rsi', 'main', 'macd'];
var _screenerLoaded = { breakout: false, patterns: false };
```

Persist user preferences via `localStorage` (e.g., chart pane order, theme).

## Major Template Pages

| Template | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `chat.html` | Main chat interface with SSE streaming |
| `trading.html` | Trading dashboard: charts, screener, patterns, portfolio |
| `brain.html` | AI Brain dashboard: learning reports, patterns, evidence modals |
| `planner.html` | Project planner with tasks, labels, members |
| `home.html` | Home dashboard with household features |

## PWA

- `manifest.json` in `app/static/`
- Service worker `sw.js`: cache-first for CDN assets, network-first for API calls
- Icons: `icon-192.png`, `icon-512.png`
